POE api(grabbing items, stats), steam api(connect with available friends)
POE api: Public stash tab API is a basic JSON interface to obtain information relevant for general trade using Premium Stash Tabs for PC clients. 
Basically the interface serves global update information (considerable as a update-"stream") on any public stash tabs recognized by the game servers.
Steam Api: (https://steamcommunity.com/dev) possible social interaction, see games people are playing that play path, see acheivements, 

